query:
SET @sd_id = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name LIKE '%San Diego%' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1);

-- More Medical Protocols
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, protocolEffectiveDate, protocolYear, createdAt)
VALUES 
(@sd_id, 'S-133', 'Diabetic Emergencies', 'Medical', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Diabetic Emergencies. Hypoglycemia treatment with dextrose and glucagon, hyperglycemia assessment.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-134', 'Poisoning / Overdose', 'Medical', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Poisoning and Overdose. Naloxone, supportive care, and specific antidotes.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-135', 'Seizures', 'Medical', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Seizures. Benzodiazepine administration and airway protection.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-136', 'Respiratory Distress', 'Respiratory', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Respiratory Distress. Assessment-based treatment, bronchodilators, CPAP, and airway management.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-138', 'Shock', 'Medical', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Shock. Fluid resuscitation and vasopressor support.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),

-- Trauma Protocols
(@sd_id, 'S-139', 'Trauma', 'Trauma', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Trauma. Primary survey, hemorrhage control, spinal motion restriction, and trauma center transport criteria.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-139A', 'Adult Traumatic Cardiac Arrest', 'Trauma', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Adult Traumatic Cardiac Arrest. Fluid bolus, no epinephrine, and rapid transport.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-141', 'Pain Management', 'Medical', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Pain Management. Fentanyl and morphine administration guidelines.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-142', 'Behavioral Emergencies', 'Medical', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Behavioral Emergencies. De-escalation and chemical restraint.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-143', 'Nausea / Vomiting', 'Medical', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Nausea and Vomiting. Ondansetron administration.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-144', 'Stroke and Transient Ischemic Attack', 'Medical', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Stroke and TIA. BE-FAST screening, FAST-ED severity scale, and stroke center transport.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-145', 'Environmental Emergencies', 'Environmental', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Environmental Emergencies. Hyperthermia, hypothermia, and drowning.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),

-- OB Protocols
(@sd_id, 'S-163', 'Obstetrical Emergencies', 'Obstetrical', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Obstetrical Emergencies. Normal delivery, cord prolapse, breech, and postpartum hemorrhage.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-166', 'Neonatal Resuscitation', 'Pediatric', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Neonatal Resuscitation. NRP guidelines and newborn care.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-166A', 'Newborn Assessment', 'Pediatric', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Newborn Assessment. APGAR scoring and initial stabilization.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW()),
(@sd_id, 'S-169', 'Pediatric Assessment', 'Pediatric', 'San Diego County EMS Treatment Protocol for Pediatric Assessment. Age-appropriate assessment techniques.', 'https://www.sandiegocounty.gov/content/dam/sdc/ems/Policies_Protocols/2025/2025-2026%20Protocol%20Packet.pdf', '2025-07-01', 2025, NOW());
